{"tid":626890,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「毒撚」一詞已經證明咗現代人開始唔鍾意用腦諗嘢","createTime":"2018-04-12T13:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-13T11:57:09.000Z","uid":105678,"like":120,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"446a35d8249651672c3d37be699ccca57a79b029","tid":626890,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:16:05.000Z","msg":"形容一個人嘅性格，可以有好多唔同方式<br />\n<br />\n如果小明鍾意一個人靜靜地睇書，正常就會咁講：<br />\n<br />\n「小明知好多嘢，學富五車。」<br />\n<br />\n現代人：<br />\n<br />\n「小明成日自己摺埋睇書，勁毒囉。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n又例如張三冇戀愛經驗，但識朋友都算多，正常會咁介紹：<br />\n<br />\n「張三雖然冇囡埋身，但性格都幾好，我一直當佢係兄弟。」<br />\n<br />\n現代人：<br />\n<br />\n「佢好毒架，讀完高中都冇過囡。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知幾時開始，好多人會自稱毒撚/話人係毒撚<br />\n<br />\n冇囡就毒撚，唔鍾意講嘢又毒撚，性格內向小小又毒撚，喜愛室內活動又毒撚<br />\n<br />\n總之乜乜柒柒，都係毒撚。<br />\n<br />\n已經冇其他詞彙去形容一個人嘅個性，下下都毒撚前毒撚後，煩到PK。<br />\n<br />\n明明社會上有千千萬萬種人，但偏偏大家就鍾愛於用「毒撚」呢個字<br />\n<br />\n貪呢個字夠大包圍，每個都人都有機會中。<br />\n<br />\n只係擁有唔係團體活動嘅時間，就係毒撚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n反之，MK一詞都同樣。<br />\n<br />\n好似變成咗毒撚嘅反義詞咁，只要小明擁有張三唔鍾意嘅個性/行為，<br />\n<br />\n咁小明就係死MK，冇腦。<br />\n<br />\n搞到成個社會對立，變到得翻「毒撚」同「MK」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢兩個詞彙已經畀人當公廁咁用到臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d077df56029944f8c2b674e302fd9fab0e15df15","tid":626890,"uid":74262,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d859b2caffe5d39c5043eb56ad3a0f686380c2da","tid":626890,"uid":105678,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d077df56029944f8c2b674e302fd9fab0e15df15","tid":626890,"uid":74262,"like":5,"dislike":6,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:24:43.000Z","msg":"見過大把破過處嘅都自稱毒撚，<br />\n<br />\n而且性格外向多朋友，只係有時會睇下動漫咁。<br />\n<br />\n根本就係啲人唔鍾意用腦諗下、反思下自己係一個乜嘢人"},{"pid":"a688f5d35bb44b266c9b73b209ae57b254dcab8a","tid":626890,"uid":89282,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"sad but true,但你咁認真係到開post都做唔到D咩，係現實識返D高汁人做朋友算啦。呢個世界大把呢D人。 If it ain't broke,don't fix it"},{"pid":"f837cd2b0d5fd5cde536729475a66ec99f6e447c","tid":626890,"uid":89282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a688f5d35bb44b266c9b73b209ae57b254dcab8a","tid":626890,"uid":89282,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:29:38.000Z","msg":"sad but true,但你咁認真係到開post都做唔到D咩，係現實識返D高汁人做朋友算啦。呢個世界大把呢D人。 If it ain't broke,don't fix it"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T13:31:47.000Z","msg":"你同佢地做既唔一樣，鐘意既野唔同，佢就會搵位入你，label你係毒撚or mk etc 咩都可以。華人係咁，好撚顛。"},{"pid":"1789abef94d057717e10b3f26bd6c49d1e9750d0","tid":626890,"uid":88366,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:21:26.000Z","msg":"第一，個社會鐘意以一個人溝唔溝到女去評價一個人<br />\n第二，高登文化滲透現實社會<br />\n<br />\n我見外國戲啲nerd地位好似越來越高，係咪得香港nerd先越來越低<br />\n<br />\n利申9up"},{"pid":"f73965429b9ac4b2c4fc78f6d92e13f983df8879","tid":626890,"uid":144011,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:32:28.000Z","msg":"搞到依個世界好似得兩種人，毒撚同非毒撚"},{"pid":"b4fa410c74d22f58275fe09b24e3190a403dd0cf","tid":626890,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T14:49:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eec0fb36236da2ecf2f02a98bffcd49bbf37a290","tid":626890,"uid":95784,"like":0